contentrichtext.text: {{wiktionary|Sula|sula}} '''Sula''' may refer to: {{tocright}} ==Places== === Norway === * [[Sula, Møre og Romsdal]], an island and a municipality * [[Sula, Sogn og Fjordane]], an island in Solund municipality * [[Sula, Sør-Trøndelag]], an island group in Frøya municipality * [[Indre Sula]] and [[Ytre Sula]], two mountains in Surnadal municipality === Other locations === * [[Sula, Iran]], a village in Semnan Province, Iran * [[Sula, Montana]], a census-designated place in the United States * [[Sula Islands]] in Indonesia * [[Sula River]] in eastern Europe, tributary of the Dnieper River * [[Sula River (Mezen)]] in northern Russia, tributary of the Mezen River * [[Sula Sgeir]], an island group in Scotland * [[San Pedro Sula]], a city in Honduras ==Other uses== * [[Booby]], a seabird in the ''Sula'' genus * [[Sula (novel)|''Sula'' (novel)]], a 1974 novel by Toni Morrison * ''Sula'', a 1969 children's novel by [[Lavinia Derwent]], with three sequels * ''[[Sula II]]'', a boat that runs trips to the island bird sanctuaries off North Berwick, Scotland * Caroline Sula, a character in ''[[Dread Empire's Fall]]'', a space-opera trilogy {{disambiguation}}
